Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:03.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started with the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:05.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting and searching\nfor our dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a strong bond\nis formed between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:08.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bright future begins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:13.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is just one way of\ndefeating the invincible Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:15.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now,\NKikyo, Naraku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:19.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha and all the rest of us connected\nto this story gather!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final shard guides us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other side of the well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:24.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new day awaits in\nthe age of warring states!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dead parasite chrysalis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:21.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So the rumors among\nthe villagers were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They said that seven days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:26.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the mountain disappeared\novernight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does this have something to do\nwith the parasite chrysalis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's faint, but there's a lingering\nsmell of Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:34.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the smell of {\i1}demons....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which permeates the soil here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:56.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! No matter how many I kill,\nthere's no end in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:57.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:06.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you find the nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But just what are these bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Parasite chrysalis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:18.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They use giant demons as\ntheir {\i1}hosts....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:20.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there's no way they'd\nbuild nests outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're awfully familiar with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What else do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't act innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did Naraku order us to\nkill the parasite chrysalis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,immediately upon finding them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't....know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:38.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saimyosho....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:42.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're telling us to go back.\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You really haven't heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:51.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unlike me, you have Naraku's {\i1}trust....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't imagine this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mountain really moved\njust now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:09.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The parasite chrysalis had\nno place to go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It means they couldn't live any longer\ninside a large demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:23.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku ordered us to kill the\nparasite chrysalis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:26.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}because he did not want\nthis to be known.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mountain that moves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the host of those parasite chrysalis?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:36.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:41.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She has a bad habit of\nwillfully going off on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That mountain is alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does he plan to\nstart this time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't understand why
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku keeps such\nan unreliable woman alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:57.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku orders this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Save Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:02.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's near!\NI smell a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:10.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:11.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}mountain....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:34.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you Naraku's henchman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the name of the fool
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who entered my body and\ndisturbed my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:55.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku entered this demon's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:05.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After deeply inhaling his filthy aura\nand miasma,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:08.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was awakened from my\N200-year slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does this mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He stole the protective stone\nfrom within my body and escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Protective stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you are hiding him,\NI will not spare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Idiot! We're after Naraku, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me where Naraku is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise, my ire will not subside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I already told you I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm looking for Naraku, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:41.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You just said that Naraku stole\nyour protective stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this protective stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:48.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The stone that is essential for me,\NGakusanjin, to exist in this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The stone that allows me to continue\nmy sleep as a {\i1}mountain....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Fuyoheki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fuyoheki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master {\i1}Gakusanjin....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:00.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Fuyoheki is the stone\nthat keeps you passive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is my protective {\i1}stone....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which dissipates my miasma\nand keeps enemies from approaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:08.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so that I will not engage in\nunnecessary battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:09.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His miasma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dissipates it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we get a hold of the Fuyoheki,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,will it mean that Naraku's miasma\nwill also disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:18.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he can hide himself from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:22.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what kind of shape\nis this Fuyoheki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What color? Does it have a scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get it back for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I do not trust such words!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit! Do you always wake up\nin such a bad mood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We ain't gonna hear anything\nmore from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:07:59.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's just no sense in\nour fighting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have only one enemy: Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If in our pursuit of Naraku\nwe find the Fuyoheki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we will return it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:25.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:29.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are crystals of my miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grab a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you are near the Fuyoheki,\nthe crystals' aura will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you move away from it,\nthe aura will reappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:47.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This will help in locating Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems he trusts us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:51.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0} Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enough. Go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But that {\i1}Naraku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did he steal something\nlike the Fuyoheki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's he gonna use it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:15.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, we're having a hard time\nlooking for Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why does he still need to\nhide his miasma?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:24.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm starting to figure it out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Naraku is gonna use the\NFuyoheki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:32.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}to camouflage that infant's miasma\nand keep him hidden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanna is supposed to be\nwith the infant...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll finally find it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:55.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura said that if the infant is found,\NNaraku can be killed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:00.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Finish them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The blessed lock of Mistress\NKikyo's hair is unraveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is something {\i1}nearby....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shikigami? But whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are {\i1}Naraku's....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense the Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just one shard!\NIt's Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:38.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard keeps\nyou alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:42.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does Naraku control your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:45.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you obey Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your soul {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The aura is disappearing from\NGakusanjin's crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean that\nthe Fuyoheki is up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then Naraku is there, {\i1}too....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only that!\NI'm starting to smell Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:16.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Kikyo.\NSince Mt. Hakurei, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:17.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:22.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I truly believed that I had\nkilled you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:26.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Things won't always go\nthe way you expect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't notice that he was\nstanding right behind me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't sense his presence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, I don't sense\NNaraku's miasma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does this mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't grasp my next {\i1}arrow....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you staring at, Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take Kikyo's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:04.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you hesitating, Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot sense Naraku's miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that the power of the\NFuyoheki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:20.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll purify it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:35.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't sense Naraku's miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He stole the Fuyoheki in order\nto come after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:56.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuyoheki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A protective stone that\nmakes miasma disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:07.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,although Kikyo was his target,\NNaraku seemed unusually casual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's happening again,\nbut are you okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo is not the type\nto travel with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're probably saying\ntheir goodbyes, like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It sure is a long farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:41.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're always with Inuyasha,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Kikyo is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It sure is taking long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what\nthey're talking about...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then Naraku was a decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Probably....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:00.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My shikigami had found\nsomething else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:01.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku did not die\nby my arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0} Ever since Mt. Hakurei,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he won't die no matter how\nmany times I hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It means his heart is\nsomewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His {\i1}heart....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:21.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's what he's trying\nto hide with the Fuyoheki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:27.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to destroy Naraku,\NI guess I must find his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This Fuyoheki will mask\nyour miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:45.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The original owner said that\nit was to keep him from senseless fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph! Now how will you use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:03.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, {\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Human souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:06.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Human souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So many of them were eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon, Haku, ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's hunt him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Slit open his belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care that you don't\ndamage his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it? There's something\nshiny inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is a human haku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:40.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Haku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The lives of the people he ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought that since we had\nthese crystals that sense miasma,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:53.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we could catch up to\NNaraku easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what Kikyo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:01.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all you spoke to\NKikyo about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:04.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:09.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case, they didn't\nhave to huddle together like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:11.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looked suspicious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:18.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The air feels heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us endure {\i1}it....{\i0}\NIt happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:23.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I smell a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Corpses of demons scattered\n{\i1}everywhere....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell are these demons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:47.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like a combination\nof various demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the soul of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, that's the Haku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All humans, animals and demons\nhave within them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Haku and Kon spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kon is the heart, or soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Haku is the power\nto move the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to the Kon\nof this demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was probably released\nwhen it died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:13.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So only the Haku kept\nthe demon moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:19.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, as long as the Haku exists,\neven a dead, soul-less body can move?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could Naraku be involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The corpses of the demons are\nscattered in four directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe this demon isn't the only one\nwith a Haku that keeps him moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:38.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:46.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can smell 'em!\NThere're still lots of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Another one, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're looking\nmore human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:29.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Compared to the earlier ones, {\i1}it's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:30.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:34.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's as though the earlier demons\nwere all {\i1}tests....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:37.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This smell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's that Hakudoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you sniffed me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:47.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you planning this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ask Moryomaru here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}demon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are getting closer and closer\nto humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I created many and tested {\i1}them....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it's easier to make them move\nwhen they're more like humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With human haku, human bodies\nwork best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:15.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's all your doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moryomaru, fight Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:22.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You intend to test him out\nwith Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:28.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll use you to practice some\nnew moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moryomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Adamant Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So he disappeared on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:46.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why the surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:58.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I created Moryomaru from\nvarious demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Making him fly was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He just flew away to\navoid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:09.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not like he deflected\nmy Adamant Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:13.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take one more blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Adamant-!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:18.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:22.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'll be devoured by\NMoryomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Devoured? Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adamant....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He broke away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi protected Moryomaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:54.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:05.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}okay....{\i0}\NI'm not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:09.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But... he outsmarted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He stole the demon crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was our way of\nfinding the {\i1}Fuyoheki....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The main thing is that\nyou're not hurt, Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are other ways\nto find Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:27.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But that Moryomaru bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:32.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Hakudoshi even went as\nfar as protecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wasn't gonna let him\nbe destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As you asked, I stole\nthe demon crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am leaving Moryomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Use him as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moryomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will....put{\i0} a soul inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:48.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo searches for Naraku\nas does Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:50.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to destroy him,\nwe must get to his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura betrays Naraku,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:54.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and guides us to where\nthe heart is {\i1}hidden....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:57.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we are sent right into\na demon's belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:24:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will all dissolve inside\nthe demon and {\i1}disappear....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,leaving only the Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will we live or die?!\NThis is our final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:10.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Bond Between Them:\NUse the Sacred Jewel Shard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:12.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please Kagome!\NPlease sustain me!
